Description: Simple Qt-based desktop clock
 Clock is a lightweight desktop clock application built with Qt.
 It displays the current time in 12-hour format, along with the date,
 weekday, and time zone information.
 .
 Features:
  - 12-hour time display
  - Current date and weekday
  - Time zone support
  - Multi-language support (Chinese)
